title: Technic Launcher cracked (Updated Dec 11)
description:
Snapshot from Dec 11 2013

Neutered authentication
Neutered Google Analytics tracking

EXE built on Win7 64bit
JAR built on Fedora 19 64bit
For those that do not like using EXE, the JAR should work fine on Windows. Mac should also be fine with this, although I do not have and do not want a Mac to test this with.

For those limited to 1.5GB RAM option:
You MUST use 64bit Java to allow more than 1.5GB memory usage. This is not up to me. It is a limitation of Java and I cannot work around this. 

This update fixes various minor issues present in the previous release as well as the most recent issue (a major one) relating to Mojang relocating some of their files, breaking client updates.
